            ],
            "effect": "The myroga wreathes themself in raw destructive energy converted from the ley line's ambient magic. The myroga deals an additional 2d6 force damage with each of their next successful fangs, tail, and talon Strikes. Once the myroga deals damage with one of these Strikes, the energy is discharged from that body part, but not the others.",
