                "type": "stat_block_section"
              }
            ],
            "effect": "The myroga diverts some of the ley line's magic into a deadly and distant explosion. The myroga creates a detonation of force in a 5-foot square within a mile of their ley line and that they can see, dealing 5d6 force damage to creatures in the area (DC 24 basic Reflex save). A myroga can create the detonation anywhere within a mile of the ley line, possibly allowing them to ignore cover the target might have from, for example, an obstacle between itself and the myroga.",
            "links": [
              {
                "alt": "basic",
                "aonid": 2297,
                "game-obj": "Rules",
                "name": "basic",
                "type": "link"
              }
            ],
            "name": "Ley Line Rupture",
            "requirement": "The myroga is within 500 feet of a ley line",
